---
/**
 * Data — src/pages/data.astro
 *
 * Phase 4D: restructured to mirror the official site's 16-dataset list in
 * three groups (population and socioeconomic, environmental, mobility).
 * Source of record: full crawl of 3mip.weebly.com data page, June 2026;
 * reflected in docs/FACTS.md § Datasets.
 *
 * Data-extension policy (official, corrected in 4D): the list may be
 * expanded, but any new dataset must be made known and available to ALL
 * teams — additions go through project coordination. The earlier
 * "document your own additions in your submission" framing was wrong and
 * has been removed.
 */
